headline: Rise in U.K. Gilt Yields Mirror Increase in U.S. Treasury Yields
summary: The rise in gilt yields has mirrored a rise in Treasury yields, Quilter Investors said, adding that a key factor remained the sheer size of bond sales by the U.K. government and the BOE that “foreign investors typically mop up.”
